des:
Access your Hey Jude account from your Echo devices. Never has your voice been more powerful!

Hey Jude us the fastest, most affordable virtual assistant service that is backed by real humans. No negotiating, no waiting, just send us your requests and we’ll get to work immediately. Like Uber makes it easy to get a ride, Hey Jude makes it easy to get everything else done.

Our agents, or Judes are on hand 24/7/365 so you can ask anything and we do everything.

Whether it is for restaurant bookings, travel, ordering food, finding a product or organising a tradesman, we will find it, quote it, deliver it & even pay for it on your behalf.

*We have human interaction
The Hey Jude platform incorporates the latest in Artificial Intelligence, but our Judes are eating, sleeping (but not on the job), breathing humans.

*We get you the best deals
We have over 150 000 vetted suppliers, ensuring you get the best deals.

*We make it safe and secure
Our platform offers safe and secure payment methods.

*We save you time
Hey Jude does not only save you money and but more importantly time, something money can’t buy.
